data.description: Just a few blocks away from Arkansas State University. This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom home has 1,632 SqFt sitting on a large corner lot. The open kitchen/dining area features tons of space, and wraps around to the living room area. Recent updates include solar panels and new storm doors on the front/back doors. Other updates include new carpets, laminate hardwood flooring, paint and trim in the last 2-3 years. A perfect home for an investor or first time home buyer, Call to set a showing! Agents please see agent remarks.
